Ruth Roman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruth_Roman 0 Ruth Roman (December 22, 1922 – September 9, 1999) was an Lithuanian-American actress, principally appearing in dramas including the Alfred Hitchcock thriller Strangers on a Train (1951).
